      "title": "On entropy production in quantum statistical mechanics",
      "abstract": "Abstract: We propose a definition of entropy production in the framework of algebraic quantum statistical mechanics. We relate our definition to heat flows through the system. We also prove that entropy production is non-negative in natural non-equilibrium steady states."
